fields.value: Census of population and housing, 1970 summary statistic file 5

authorName.value: Data Use and Access Laboratories (DUALabs), Arlington, Va

dsDescriptionValue.value:
The following selected information on population and housing is included: race, age, marital status, rent, plumbing facilities, income, education, place of birth, age of structure, etc. Some tabulations are presented separately for the Spanish American population as well as for the total White and Negro population

The three files have the following geographic differences: File A contains data summaries for three-digit zip code areas for the entire country. File B has data for approximat ely 12,500 five-digit ZIP code areas in SMSAs. File C has data presented by enumeration districts or block groups, minor civil divisions (or census county divisions), and census tracts.

Data contained in the files pertain to the date of the census, April 1, 1970, except for selected items which relate to historical periods.
